headline: HSBC downgrades HP Inc to 'hold' on cost pressures, trims price target
summary: Investing.com -- HSBC downgraded HP Inc (NYSE:HPQ) to "hold" from "buy," given the near-term cost pressures in the PC segment that are expected to weigh on profitability in the first half of fiscal 2025.
